index.title: High Five Goodbye
index.description: At the end of their first date, April and Ben are parting ways when instead of a kiss, Ben goes in for an awkward high-five. In that moment a piece of ultra-sticky gum falls from the sky cementing their hands together. Fate just made this date a whole lot longer.
index.starring: Scott Patey, Athena Russell, Tiarra Sulyk, Brandon Jason Miller, Hannah Rochelle Burr, Zia Marashi, Stephi Chin-Salvo, Kougar Vakarian, Megs Calleja
